y Network, Inc." /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.434549.b, Gene Security Network, Inc., 2686 Middlefield Road, Redwood City, CA, 94063, USA" /></span></sup>, </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-6">Bradley E Bernstein</a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff4">4</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Harvard Medical School" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.38142.3c, 000000041936754X, Molecular Pathology Unit and Center for Cancer Research, Massachusetts General Hospital and Department of Pathology, Harvard Medical School, 13th Street, Charlestown, MA, 02129, USA" /></span>,<a href="#Aff5">5</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Broad Institute of Harvard and MIT" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.66859.34, Broad Institute of Harvard and MIT, 7 Cambridge Center, Cambridge, MA, 02142, USA" /></span></sup>, </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-7">Chad Nusbaum</a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff5">5</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Broad Institute of Harvard and MIT" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.66859.34, Broad Institute of Harvard and MIT, 7 Cambridge Center, Cambridge, MA, 02142, USA" /></span></sup>, </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-8">Richard M Myers</a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff6">6</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Stanford University Medical Center" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.240952.8, 0000000087342732, Department of Genetics, Stanford University Medical Center, Stanford, CA, 94305, USA" /></span></sup>, </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-9">Myles Brown</a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff2">2</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Brigham and Women's Hospital and Harvard Medical School" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.62560.37, 0000000403788294, Division of Molecular and Cellular Oncology, Department of Medical Oncology, Dana-Farber Cancer Institute and Department of Medicine, Brigham and Women's Hospital and Harvard Medical School, 44 Binney Street, Boston, MA, 02115, USA" /></span></sup>, </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-10" data-corresp-id="c1">Wei Li<svg width="16" height="16" class="u-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#global-icon-email"></use></svg></a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff7">7</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Baylor College of Medicine" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.39382.33, 000000012160926X, Division of Biostatistics, Dan L Duncan Cancer Center, Department of Molecular and Cellular Biology, Baylor College of Medicine, One Baylor Plaza, Houston, TX, 77030, USA" /></span></sup> &amp; </li><li class="c-author-list__item" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a data-test="author-name" data-track="click" data-track-action="open author" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link" href="#auth-11" data-corresp-id="c2">X Shirley Liu<svg width="16" height="16" class="u-icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#global-icon-email"></use></svg></a></span><sup class="u-js-hide"><a href="#Aff1">1</a><span itemprop="affiliation" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="u-visually-hidden"><meta itemprop="name" content="Dana-Farber Cancer Institute and Harvard School of Public Health" /><meta itemprop="address" content="grid.38142.3c, 000000041936754X, Department of Biostatistics and Computational Biology, Dana-Farber Cancer Institute and Harvard School of Public Health, 44 Binney Street, Boston, MA, 02115, USA" /></span></sup> </li></ul>
                            <p class="c-article-info-details" data-container-section="info">
                                
    <a data-test="journal-link" href="/"><i data-test="journal-title">Genome Biology</i></a>

                                <b data-test="journal-volume"><span class="u-visually-hidden">volume</span> 9</b>, Article number: <span data-test="article-number">R137</span> (<span data-test="article-publication-year">2008</span>)
            <a href="#citeas" class="c-article-info-details__cite-as u-hide-print" data-track="click" data-track-action="cite this article" data-track-category="article body" data-track-label="link">Cite this article</a>
